#### 2. No Authentication or Authorization (OWASP A01 – Broken Access Control)
**Lines 11–16** — The `/users` endpoint is completely unauthenticated. Any caller can enumerate all user data. There is also no role-based access control.

```js
// ✅ Add an auth middleware (e.g., JWT verification)
const authenticateToken = (req, res, next) => {
  const token = req.headers['authorization']?.split(' ')[1];
  if (!token) return res.status(401).json({ error: 'Unauthorized' });
