#### 5. No CORS Policy (OWASP A05 – Security Misconfiguration)
Without explicit CORS headers, Express will either block legitimate cross-origin callers or — depending on proxy config — allow all origins implicitly. Either extreme is wrong.

```js
// ✅ Use cors (npm install cors)
const cors = require('cors');
app.use(cors({
  origin: process.env.ALLOWED_ORIGINS?.split(',') ?? [],
