#### 5. No CORS Policy
Express has no CORS headers configured. Browsers will apply the same-origin policy, but this is not explicitly enforced by the server. If this API is ever accessed cross-origin, any origin would be implicitly allowed by some proxy configurations.

**Recommendation:** Be explicit about what origins are allowed:

```js
const cors = require('cors');

app.use(cors({
  origin: process.env.ALLOWED_ORIGIN || 'https://yourdomain.com',
