This fingerprints your tech stack for attackers.

**b) No security headers at all** — no `Content-Security-Policy`, no `X-Frame-Options`, no `X-Content-Type-Options`, no `Strict-Transport-Security`.

**Recommendation:** Add [`helmet`](https://helmetjs.github.io/) as the very first middleware:

```js
